high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then turn right to face the cabinet.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the top of the cabinet.
Turn right and walk forward towards the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn off the water and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right to face the cabinet.
Put the clean bar of soap on top of the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on top of a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and face the tall cabinet on the right.
Pick up the soap from the back of the cabinet.
Hold the soap and turn to the right.
Place the soap in the sink on the left and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the soap.
Hold the soap and turn around and face the cabinet.
Place the soap to the front of the cabinet, on top.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a bar of soap and place on a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and straight, turning right to face the counter with the white spray bottle on it.
Pick up the soap on the counter.
Turn right and look at the sink.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Turn around and face the counter again.
Place the soap on the counter in front of and to the left of the spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a counter.
